  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to learn if a new 7 day patch ECG recording monitor can
      serve the same purpose as standard monitoring systems. The new 7day patch is significantly
      smaller and lighter than previous ECG recorders.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this research is to evaluate ECG signal quality of the BDx 7 day ECG
      Patch heart monitor after 7 full days of wear, establishing that the device is safe and
      effective to wear for up to 7 days.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
